      "id": "mem-MEMORY-stomp-websocket-auth--critical",
      "content": "### Authentication flow\n1. HTTP upgrade: permitted (no auth at HTTP level, `/ws/**` is `permitAll`)\n2. CONNECT frame: `StompAuthChannelInterceptor.preSend()` validates JWT, stores `CocroAuthentication` in WebSocket session attributes under:\n   - `SESSION_AUTH_KEY` (\"COCRO_AUTH\") → for SecurityContextHolder restoration\n   - `SimpMessageHeaderAccessor.USER_HEADER` (\"simpUser\") → for DefaultSimpUserRegistry\n3. SEND/SUBSCRIBE frames: `beforeHandle()` (ExecutorChannelInterceptor) restores to Security",
